&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Required Qualifications&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Research Specialist Experience Requirement: Bachelors or Masters degree and 8+ years of industry experience.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Sr Scientist Experience Requirements: &amp;nbsp;PhD and 6+ years post-PhD, PLUS 3+ years of industry experience.&lt;/li&gt;
