&lt;p&gt;An exciting opportunity is available for a &lt;strong&gt;Senior Scientist I / II&lt;/strong&gt;&amp;nbsp;to join the Institute of Medicine (IOM) Drug Discovery and Development Sciences team at Altos Labs.We are seeking a very highly motivated, creative, and collaborative individual who is passionate and dedicated to employing their scientific knowledge to help restore cell health and resilience to reverse disease.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
